eedbackModal_main_3616928\" data-toggle=\"modal\" role=\"button\" tabindex=\"0\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-feedback\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-feedback\"></use></svg><span class=\"zDocsFeedbackButtonText\"> Feedback</span></span></div></div><div class=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><button aria-label=\"Show topic actions\" data-toggle=\"dropdown\" id=\"zDocsTopicActionsMobile\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-ellipsis-h\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-ellipsis-h\"></use></svg></button><div class=\"dropdown-menu zDocsDropdownMenu zDocsTopicActionsMobileDropdown dropdown-menu-right\"></div></div><div style=\"flex-basis: 100%; height: 0px;\"></div><ul class=\"zDocsTopicPageDetails\"><li class=\"zDocsTopicPageDate css-cinqea\">Last Updated<span class=\"css-cinqea\">Okt 09, 2024</span></li><li class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryDetailsItem\"><button class=\"zDocsAiTopicSummaryButton\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-topic-summary\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-topic-summary\"></use></svg>Summarize</button></li><li class=\"spacer\" role=\"presentation\"></li><div class=\"zDocsLabelWrapper\"><ul><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: Uniface\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=prod_uniface\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>Uniface</a></li><li class=\"zDocsLabel\"><a aria-describedby=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" class=\"css-ettsdk\" data-tooltip-content=\"Search all site by tag: 10.4\" data-tooltip-id=\"hyperLinkFacetsTooltip\" href=\"/de-DE/search?labelkey=uniface_10.4\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-label=\"Tag\" class=\"ico-tag\" role=\"img\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-tag\"></use></svg>10.4</a></li></ul></div></ul></header><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBody\" data-prismjs-copy=\"Copy\" data-prismjs-copy-error=\"Copy failed! Use Ctrl + C instead.\" data-prismjs-copy-success=\"Copied!\"><div class=\"zDocsTopicPageBodyContent\" dir=\"ltr\"><div id=\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104xgk1665702581092.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgk1665702581092.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/xgk1665702581092.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"xgk1665702581092\" role=\"article\">\n<div class=\"body conbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">Form instance property that determines whether the popup window is displayed relative to a field or the mouse pointer. This property can be set in ProcScript using <span class=\"keyword cmdname\">newinstance</span>.\n </p>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__p_d100310e1_d100311e1_d100312e1\"></p>\n<section class=\"section refsyn\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__topic_d100313e1_d100314e1_d100315e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__p_d100316e1_d100317e1_d100318e1\">PopupAt\n                                                <code class=\"ph codeph\">=</code>\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">field</code> | <code class=\"ph codeph\">mouse</code>\n</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__section_w4308ab1b5b5_w4309ab1b5_w4310ab1\">\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__table_d11708e1_d11709e1_d11710e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__table_d11708e1_d11709e1_d11710e1__entry__1\">\n Value\n </th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__table_d11708e1_d11709e1_d11710e1__entry__2\">\n Description\n </th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgk1665702581092__table_d11708e1_d11709e1_d11710e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph defvalue\">field</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgk1665702581092__table_d11708e1_d11709e1_d11710e1__entry__2\">\n The popup window is displayed relative to the field specified by the FieldName property. If FieldName is not specified, it is relative to the current field.\n </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgk1665702581092__table_d11708e1_d11709e1_d11710e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">mouse</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"xgk1665702581092__table_d11708e1_d11709e1_d11710e1__entry__2\">\n The popup window is displayed relative to the mouse pointer. The FieldName is ignored.\n </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section table\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__section_5ab25d8431d1a6b51d3c89f655c8b0b6\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d101254e128\">Usage</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__table_d11717e1_d11718e1_d11719e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dynamic? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Yes </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Supported in Grid? </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> No </td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\"> Dependencies: </td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\">Applicable only if windowtype=\n                           <code class=\"ph codeph\">popup</code>. </td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section p\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__section_w4311ab1b5b9_w4312ab1b5_w4313ab1\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d101254e177\">Description</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__p_d100325e1_d100326e1_d100327e1\">The PopupAt property controls whether the popup window is displayed relative to an object or mouse cursor, but the Postion property determines the precise positioning.</p>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section ul\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__section_03f1f54cc6bca0bab15754bd233b16e4\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d101254e187\">Applies To</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__ul_gnj_5hx_swb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"xgk1665702581092__li_d40493e1_d40494e1_d40495e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"rhe1665702581016.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/rhe1665702581016.html\" title=\"A popup window displays a form in a secondary window that is anchored to a field. The position of the popup window is configurable, so that it can be displayed outside or inside the boundaries of its parent field.\">Popup Window</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div><div class=\"contentPlaceholder\" style=\"height: 500px;\"><div class=\"contentContainer zDocsSideBoxes\"><div><h5 aria-level=\"5\" class=\"css-g931ng\">Related Links</h5><ul><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jcx1665702581523.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>Position</a><p>Form instance property that defines the position of a popup form relative to its anchor object, which can be a field, popup rectangle, or mouse cursor. The value specifies an edge or corner from which the window starts, and the direction in which it is displayed. This property can be set in ProcScript using newinstance and $windowproperties.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ryt1665702577808.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>newinstance</a><p>Creates a new instance of a component.</p></li><li><a class=\"css-ettsdk\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/bch1665702773514.html\" stylesprops=\"[object Object]\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-related-link\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-related-link\"></use></svg>$windowproperties</a><p>Set or return the current window properties of a Form instance.</p></li></ul></div></div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616928\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3616928\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "PopupAt Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Form instance property that determines whether the popup window is displayed relative to a field or the mouse pointer. This property can be set in ProcScript using newinstance . PopupAt = field | mouse Value Description field The popup window is displayed relative to the field specified by the FieldName property. If FieldName is not specified, it is relative to the current field. mouse The popup window is displayed relative to the mouse pointer. The FieldName is ignored. Usage Dynamic? Yes Supported in Grid? No Dependencies: Applicable only if windowtype= popup . Description The PopupAt property controls whether the popup window is displayed relative to an object or mouse cursor, but the Postion property determines the precise positioning. Applies To Popup Window Related Links Position Form instance property that defines the position of a popup form relative to its anchor object, which can be a field, popup rectangle, or mouse cursor. The value specifies an edge or corner from which the window starts, and the direction in which it is displayed. This property can be set in ProcScript using newinstance and $windowproperties. newinstance Creates a new instance of a component. $windowproperties Set or return the current window properties of a Form instance. Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}